      • getRange

        Range getRange(Cell upLeft,
             Cell downRight)
        Method to get a rectangular part of a sheet as a Range.
        Parameters:
        upLeft - is the first cell in the expected range
        downRight - is the last cell in the expected range
        Returns:

      • getRange

        Range getRange(int colLeft,
             int rowUp,
             int colRight,
             int rowDown)
        Method to get a rectangular part of a sheet as a Range.
        Parameters:
        rowUp - is the row index of the upper left cell in the range
        colLeft - is the column index of the upper left cell in the range
        rowDown - is the row index of the last cell in the range
        colRight - is the column index of the last cell in the range
        Returns:
        an array of cells with all the cells in the range from cell(rowUp, colLeft) to cell(rowDown, colRight)
